      "body" : "More specifically, this particular rule is mentioned here: <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/third%5Fedition/html/expressions.html#239829\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Multiplicative Operators</a>, so let it stand here for future reference."
