    "answer_id" : 787709,
    "question_id" : 787700,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>You can cast even just one of them, but for consistency you may want to explicitly cast both so something like v = (float)s / (float)t should work. </p>\n"
  }, {
