    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>class CalcV \n{\n      float v;\n      float calcV(int s, int t)\n      {\n          float value1=s;\n          float value2=t;\n          v = value1 / value2;\n          return v;\n      } //end calcV\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
